    <item>
      <title>Rokid Glasses AI 眼鏡殺入香港，支援廣東話語音 + 採光波技術顯示更即時</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/08/14/rokidglasses-hk-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=rokidglasses-hk-launch</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/08/14/rokidglasses-hk-launch/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>Edward</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Aug 2025 03:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>科技新聞</category>
      <category>AI</category>
      <category>Rokid</category>
      <category>Rokid Glasses</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1321180</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;近年隨著 AI 愈來愈盛行，智能穿戴裝置，例如：耳機、眼鏡等又再次開始受人注目，不過之前的產品就算引入 AI 功能，但不支援廣東話語音操控始終是死症。近日就有代理引入支援廣東話的智能 AI 眼鏡，而且功能多多，現在就讓 Edward 帶大家去現場睇睇啦。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;中國 AR 眼鏡龍頭，鏡身夠輕不夾頭&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;話説今次新推出的智能眼鏡名為 Rokid Glasses，是由中國 AR 眼鏡龍頭品牌之一的 Rokid（樂奇）最新推出，而今次這款 AI 眼鏡就與中國時尚太陽眼鏡品牌 Bolon 聯手設計，它的重量只有 49g，而且設有可調節的鼻託及鏡臂，官方表示即使全天佩戴亦感覺自在，Edward 就親身戴過，即使頭大如我但戴上 Rokid Glasses 亦不太覺一對鏡臂「夾頭」，算是舒服，而且鏡身確實頗輕身，長時間佩戴應該問題亦不大。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141557-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141557-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141557.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321219" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151752-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151752-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151752.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Rokid Glasses 是由中國 AR 眼鏡龍頭品牌之一的 Rokid（樂奇）最新推出，眼鏡鏡框採用了鋁鎂合金物料製造，並加入了 1.7mm 超薄高強度鏡片。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321220" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141628-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141628-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141628.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲鏡臂設有內置喇叭，它使用了 TR90 彈性鏡臂，而且加入了鋼琴烤漆質感，而鏡臂與鏡身亦使用了高精度鈦合金轉軸，十分實淨。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142357-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142357-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142357.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_144310-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_144310-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_144310.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲由於鏡臂具有彈性，筆者試過即使頭部較大的用家佩戴，也不會有夾頭感，算是舒服。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152642-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152642-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152642.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲不過鏡片在某些角度會有點反光。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141613-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141613-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141613.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Rokid Glasses 這款 AI 眼鏡與中國時尚太陽眼鏡品牌 Bolon 聯手設計，重量只有 49g。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152022-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152022-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152022.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲官方表示 Rokid Glasses 在中度混合使用情況下，續航力有約 8 至 10 小時，算是可以接受。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;集結多個 AI 模型首支援廣東話&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rokid Glasses 內建了針對高階智能眼鏡運算能力而設的 Qualcomm Snapdragon AR1+ Gen 1 晶片，而且內建了多個 AI 模型，包括：通義千問、豆包、智譜清言、DeekSeek、奈米搜尋等（官方表示不同地區會有相應相容的 AI 模型），可為用家以 AR 技術投射模式提供文字翻譯、物體識別、拍照答題、語音轉錄文字等功能，而稍後十月更會推出實時導航功能。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151939-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151939-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151939.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Rokid Glasses 內建了針對高階智能眼鏡運算能力而設的 Qualcomm Snapdragon AR1+ Gen 1 晶片。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1321212 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142558-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142558-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142558.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲它亦內建了多個 AI 模型，包括：通義千問、豆包、智譜清言、DeekSeek、奈米搜尋等（官方表示不同地區會有相應相容的 AI 模型），可為用家以 AR 技術投射模式提供文字翻譯、物體識別、拍照答題、語音轉錄文字等功能。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142650-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142650-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142650.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲眼鏡甚至可以進行會議紀錄功能。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153028-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153028-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153028.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲稍後十月更會推出實時導航功能，不過似乎暫時只可支援配合高德地圖使用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;更難得的是，Rokid Glasses 支援體感及語音操控功能，前者上手簡單，例如：點頭接電話、搖頭即拒接等，而且文字翻譯方面更支援多達 89 種語言，當中最難得肯定是不只支援普通話，更支援以廣東話進行語音操控，亦是市場上少有隻需數千元已可支援廣東話語音操控的 AR 智能眼鏡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142709-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142709-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142709.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321217" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_154324-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_154324-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_154324.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Rokid Glasses 最難得肯定是不只支援普通話，更支援以廣東話進行語音操控，亦是市場上少有隻需數千元已可支援廣東話語音操控的 AR 智能眼鏡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rokid Glasses 的另一個特點，就是內建了全球最細只有 0.15cc 的微型 LED 顯示引擎，雖然細小但已足夠用家透過鏡頭瀏覽各種資訊，而且光波亮度可高達 1500 尼特，即使在陽光下仍能清晰看到內容。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141904-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141904-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_141904.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Rokid Glasses 每邊鏡頭均內建了全球最細只有 0.15cc 的微型 LED 顯示引擎，雖然細小但已足夠用家透過鏡頭瀏覽各種資訊，而且光波亮度可高達 1500 尼特，即使在陽光下仍能清晰看到內容。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;筆者現場就試玩過，基本上戴上眼鏡後，字詞語句會出現在眼鏡中間下一點的位置，用家無需刻意向下望已可看清所有內容，而且字體十分清晰，體驗不錯。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152351-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152351-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152351.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;配合眼鏡近乎即時的文字翻譯功能，即使與外國人溝通，用家也可透過眼鏡看到對方外語即時翻譯為中文的意思，令大家與易瞭解對方説話的意思。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153029-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153029-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153029.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321208" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152554-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152554-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152554.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;此外，它亦內建獨特的提詞功能，當將講稿輸入到配合使用的專屬 APP，之後戴上眼鏡，用家就可以在眼鏡上看到講稿內容，此舉令大家可以無需完全背誦講稿，仍可更有自信地完成演講或報告，只需要將心力放於與聽眾互動，提升會議成效。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153031-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153031-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_153031.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142345-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142345-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142345.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;操控簡單易上手內建鏡頭可攝錄&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;至於操控方法亦十分簡單，與其他智能眼鏡一樣，用家只需要在鏡臂側或頂部單擊、雙擊或滑動，即使點選功能或在目錄上滑動選擇內容。而在眼鏡左上角更設有一個 1,200 萬像素的高清鏡頭，亦支援低光 HDR 及 60fps 幀率拍攝功能，方便用家以第一身視角進行拍照或錄影。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142403-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142403-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142403.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲操控方法亦十分簡單，與其他智能眼鏡一樣，用家只需要在鏡臂側或頂部單擊、雙擊或滑動，即使點選功能或在目錄上滑動選擇內容。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_143907-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_143907-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_143907.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲在眼鏡左上角設有 1,200 萬像素鏡頭。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321196" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152235-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152235-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152235.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321198" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152313-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152313-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_152313.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲之後用家就可以使用這個鏡頭，以第一身視角進行拍照或錄影，之後更可透過專屬 APP 一鍵分享至不同平台，但主要是以中國社交媒體平台為主，包括：CapCut、小紅書、WeChat 等。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151834-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151834-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_151834.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲另外針對有近視或散光的用家，官方亦有推出另購的磁吸卡扣套裝。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321200" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142439-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142439-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142439.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142802-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142802-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_142802.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲只要將鏡片裝上卡扣套裝內的磁吸支柄，之後就可以吸附在 Rokid Glasses 眼鏡內側位置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;HKT 獨家預售定價公佈&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;今次推出的 Rokid Glasses 由本地代理 UNITY Tech 引入，並透過 HKT 獨家發售，暫時已開始接受預訂，定價為 $4,688。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1321192 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_150510-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_150510-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250813_150510.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
